---
import { Card, CardHeader, CardTitle, CardContent } from "@/components/ui/card";
---

<section id="about" class="py-20 bg-secondary/10">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
    <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-12 text-center text-primary">About</h2>
    <Card>
      <CardHeader>
        <CardTitle>Every great design begins with an even better story</CardTitle>
      </CardHeader>
      <CardContent>
        <p class="text-muted-foreground">
          As a passionate UX/UI designer and no-code developer, I've spent the last 9 years crafting digital experiences that not only look great but also solve real problems. My journey began with a simple belief: that great design can change the world. Since then, I've collaborated with startups and established brands to create digital solutions for both web and mobile platforms, always focusing on creating intuitive and engaging user experiences.
        </p>
      </CardContent>
    </Card>
    <div class="mt-12">
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6 text-primary">Education & Experience</h3>
      <ul class="space-y-4">
        <li>
          <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold">Freelance Designer</h4>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground">2020 - Present</p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold">Team Lead of Marketing</h4>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground">2018 - 2020</p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold">Team Lead of Marketing</h4>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground">2016 - 2018</p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold">Bachelor Degree of Information Technology</h4>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground">2012 - 2016</p>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>